        <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;This post covers the &lt;strong&gt;imgswap and img shortcodes&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;. Images can also be embedded directly using markdown &lt;code&gt;![Ferris](ferris.svg)&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;, but it is better to use a shortcode so you can explicitly set the width and height, this will help prevent content layout shift which improves user experience and the google lighthouse score.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
